title: 858. Trey Lance Breakdown, Focus on Bills & TNF Preview
itunes:title: 858. Trey Lance Breakdown, Focus on Bills & TNF Preview
description:
Daniel Jeremiah and Bucky Brooks are back with a new episode of Move the Sticks. To start off, the guys recap the Monday Night Football game between the Seahawks and Broncos. Next, the pair discuss if the 49ers should panic with quarterback Trey Lance or not. After that, the duo focus on a team that's playing unique, the Bills. Following that, the guys preview a few Week 2 matchups, the Thursday Night Football matchup of the Chargers vs. Chiefs and also the Buccaneers vs. Saints. To wrap up the show, the pair give credit to Marshall for upsetting Notre Dame on Saturday.


Move the Sticks is a part of the NFL Podcasts Network.
